text: Tosin Cole (/ˈtoʊsɪn/; born 23 July 1992) is an American-born British actor. He is known for various roles in British television series and films. He began his on-screen career starring in The Cut and EastEnders: E20, later securing a regular role as Neil Cooper in the soap opera Hollyoaks. After leaving the show Cole appeared in a range of television series and commercial films for guest appearances and participated in many short films. From 2018 to 2021, Cole starred as Ryan Sinclair in Doctor Who. Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:British actors
